---
import Header from "../../components/company/CompanyHeader.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/company/CompanyFooter.astro";

const EFFECTIVE_DATE = "October 31, 2025";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Legal Protocols • Ashak Studios</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy and Terms of Service for Ashak Studios games." />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#8D46E7" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Pixelify+Sans:wght@400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <style>
      /* --- CORE VARIABLES --- */
      :root {
        --bg-dark: #030304;
        --accent-primary: #8D46E7;
        --accent-secondary: #5A41E3;
        --text-main: #ffffff;
        --text-muted: #9ca3af;
        --card-bg: rgba(20, 20, 28, 0.75);
        --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        --radius: 24px;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background-color: var(--bg-dark);
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }

      h1, h2, h3, h4 { font-family: 'Pixelify Sans', sans-serif; }

      /* --- ANIMATED BACKGROUND --- */
      .background-fx {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
        z-index: -1;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, #1a112c 0%, #030304 70%);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .orb {
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(90px);
        opacity: 0.35;
        animation: floatOrb 12s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
      }
      .orb-1 { width: 500px; height: 500px; background: var(--accent-primary); top: -15%; left: -10%; }
      .orb-2 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: var(--accent-secondary); bottom: 10%; right: -10%; animation-delay: -4s; }

      @keyframes floatOrb {
        0% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
        100% { transform: translate(30px, 50px); }
      }

      /* --- LAYOUT & HERO --- */
      .container {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 140px 0 60px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px);
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, #a5a5a5 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(141, 70, 231, 0.3);
        line-height: 1.1;
      }

      .date-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 6px 16px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        border-radius: 100px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 13px;
        font-family: 'Inter', monospace;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
      }

      /* --- TOC NAVIGATION --- */
      .toc {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 16px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .toc-btn {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 100px;
        background: rgba(141, 70, 231, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(141, 70, 231, 0.3);
        color: #dcbfff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }
      .toc-btn:hover {
        background: var(--accent-primary);
        color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(141, 70, 231, 0.4);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      /* --- LEGAL CARD (GLASS PANEL) --- */
      .legal-card {
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        padding: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 50px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
      }

      /* Typography within Card */
      .section-title {
        font-size: 32px;
        color: #fff;
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        padding-bottom: 16px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      .section-title span { color: var(--accent-primary); }

      .meta-info {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-style: italic;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        display: block;
      }

      h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #e5e7eb;
        margin: 32px 0 12px;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }

      p, li {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: #d1d5db;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      
      ul {
        margin: 0 0 24px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        padding-left: 8px;
      }
      li::marker { color: var(--accent-primary); }

      a {
        color: var(--accent-primary);
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--accent-primary);
        transition: 0.2s;
      }
      a:hover {
        color: #fff;
        border-bottom-style: solid;
      }

      /* Highlight Box (Quick Reference) */
      .highlight-box {
        background: rgba(141, 70, 231, 0.05);
        border: 1px solid rgba(141, 70, 231, 0.3);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }
      .highlight-box h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #fff; }
      .highlight-box li { color: #e0e0e0; font-size: 15px; }
      .highlight-box strong { color: var(--accent-primary); }

      /* Animation */
      .reveal {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) forwards;
      }
      @keyframes fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

      /* Responsive */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .legal-card { padding: 24px; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 36px; }
        .section-title { font-size: 24px; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- BG FX -->
    <div class="background-fx">
      <div class="orb orb-1"></div>
      <div class="orb orb-2"></div>
    </div>

    <Header />

    <main>
      
      <!-- HERO -->
      <section class="hero container">
        <div class="date-badge reveal">Effective: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</div>
        <h1 class="reveal" style="animation-delay:0.1s">LEGAL PROTOCOLS</h1>
        
        <div class="toc reveal" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
          <a class="toc-btn" href="#privacy">
            <span>↓</span> Privacy Policy
          </a>
          <a class="toc-btn" href="#terms">
            <span>↓</span> Terms of Service
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- PRIVACY POLICY -->
      <section class="container">
        <article id="privacy" class="legal-card reveal" style="animation-delay:0.3s">
          <h2 class="section-title">Privacy Policy <span>01</span></h2>
          <span class="meta-info">Applies to: “Max On The Space” and other games published by Ashak Studios.</span>

          <h3>1) Summary</h3>
          <p>We designed our games to respect your privacy. We do not run our own backend servers for user data and we do not collect personal data from you. Your game progress and preferences are stored locally on your device. Purchases are processed by Apple using your Apple ID.</p>

          <h3>2) Data We Do <em>Not</em> Collect</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>No names, email addresses, phone numbers, or account credentials</li>
            <li>No precise location data</li>
            <li>No analytics or usage profiles stored on our servers</li>
            <li>No device-level personal identifiers stored by us</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>3) What Is Stored On Your Device</h3>
          <p>Your coin balance, hints, level progress, language preference (82 languages available), audio settings (music/SFX), and notification preference are saved locally on your device. If you delete the app, these local records are removed with it.</p>

          <h3>4) Purchases & Subscriptions (Apple ID)</h3>
          <p>In-app purchases and subscriptions are processed by Apple using your Apple ID. We receive non-personal purchase status (e.g., whether a purchase is active) from platform services in order to unlock features on your device. We do not receive your full payment information.</p>

          <h3>5) Third-Party Providers</h3>
          <p>We use third-party providers only to: (i) manage subscriptions and purchase validation, and (ii) deliver advertising where applicable. These providers operate under their own privacy policies and may process limited technical information required to provide their services. We do not combine this information with any data of our own.</p>

          <h3>6) Advertising</h3>
          <p>Our games may include advertising formats such as interstitial, native, banner, and optional rewarded ads. If you upgrade to <strong>PRO</strong>, interstitial, native, and banner ads are disabled during the active subscription period; optional rewarded ads remain available so you can choose to earn in-game rewards.</p>

          <h3>7) Children’s Privacy</h3>
          <p>Our games are suitable for a wide audience. If you are under the age required by your local law to make purchases or provide consent, please use the game with a parent or guardian.</p>

          <h3>8) Offline Use</h3>
          <p>You can open the game offline, but we <strong>do not recommend extended offline play</strong>. When offline, purchase validation and rewarded ads cannot run; coin or hint balances may appear inconsistent until connectivity is restored.</p>

          <h3>9) Internationalization</h3>
          <p>The game supports 82 languages. Minor translation inaccuracies may occur; we continuously improve localization quality.</p>

          <h3>10) Changes & Contact</h3>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect product or legal changes. If you have questions about privacy, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a>.</p>

          <!-- Highlighting the Economy Info -->
          <div class="highlight-box">
            <h3>Quick Reference: In-Game Economy</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Starting balance: <strong>120 Coins</strong></li>
              <li>Skip a level: <strong>60 Coins</strong></li>
              <li>Use a hint: <strong>30 Coins</strong></li>
              <li>Rewarded ad grant: <strong>+20 Coins</strong> (optional)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </article>

        <!-- TERMS OF SERVICE -->
        <article id="terms" class="legal-card reveal" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
          <h2 class="section-title">Terms of Service <span>02</span></h2>
          <span class="meta-info">Effective Date: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</span>

          <h3>1) About These Terms</h3>
          <p>These Terms govern your use of our mobile games, including “Max On The Space,” published by Ashak Studios (“we,” “us”). By installing or using the game, you agree to these Terms.</p>

          <h3>2) License</h3>
          <p>We grant you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use the game for entertainment on compatible devices. You may not reverse engineer, redistribute, or exploit the game commercially.</p>

          <h3>3) In-App Purchases & Subscriptions</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Platform Processing:</strong> All purchases are processed by Apple via your Apple ID. Manage/cancel subscriptions in <em>Settings &gt; Apple ID &gt; Subscriptions</em>.</li>
            <li><strong>PRO (Auto-Renew Monthly):</strong> Immediately grants <strong>+300 Coins</strong> and <strong>+10 Hints</strong>, and disables <em>interstitial</em>, <em>native</em>, and <em>banner</em> ads for one month.</li>
            <li><strong>Remove Ads (One-Time):</strong> Records a lifetime ad-removal entitlement to your Apple ID (excludes optional rewarded ads).</li>
            <li><strong>Coin Packs:</strong> 200, 600, and 1000 Coin purchases are tied to your Apple ID.</li>
            <li><strong>Refunds:</strong> We do not handle refunds directly. Requests are subject to Apple’s policies.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>4) Gameplay & Progress</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>You start with <strong>120 Coins</strong>. Skipping a level costs <strong>60 Coins</strong>; using a hint costs <strong>30 Coins</strong>.</li>
            <li>Optional rewarded ads can grant <strong>+20 Coins</strong>.</li>
            <li>You can revisit any level you have previously completed from the Levels section.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>5) Connectivity & Services</h3>
          <p>The game can run offline, but prolonged offline use is discouraged. Purchases, subscription checks, and rewarded ads require internet access. We use third-party providers to validate subscriptions and serve ads; their terms apply to their respective processing.</p>

          <h3>6) Warranties & Liability</h3>
          <p>The game is provided “as is” and “as available.” To the extent permitted by law, we disclaim warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement.</p>

          <h3>7) Age & Compliance</h3>
          <p>Comply with your local laws regarding age and purchases. If you are under the applicable age of consent, use the game under supervision of a parent or guardian.</p>

          <h3>8) Changes & Contact</h3>
          <p>We may revise these Terms when we add features or as laws change. For support or legal questions, contact: <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a></p>
        </article>

      </section>

    </main>

    <Footer />

    <!-- Reveal Animation Script -->
    <script is:inline>
      const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
        entries.forEach(entry => {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.style.animationPlayState = 'running';
            observer.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        });
      }, { threshold: 0.1 });

      document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el => {
        el.style.animationPlayState = 'paused';
        observer.observe(el);
      });
    </script>

  </body>
</html>